---
title: Truffle Mushroom Carbonara with Parsley and Cheese
description: We love good Truffle Mushroom Carbonara and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/truffle-mushroom-carbonara-fe45798c-48e44cfb.jpg
